==English==

===Noun===
'''concertina'''

#''Music.'' A musical instrument, like the various accordions, that is a member of the [[free-reed]] family of musical instruments, typically having buttons on both ends and are distinguished from an accordion (piano or button) by the direction of the button travel when pushed, traveling in the same direction as the bellows.

